# NOT a private key — placeholder only.
#
# Setup (method B):
#   1. Copy your real private key to:  secrets/ssh/id_ed25519
#   2. chmod 600 secrets/ssh/id_ed25519   (Git Bash / WSL on server copy)
#   3. In secrets/deploy.env add:
#        DEPLOY_SSH_IDENTITY_FILE=secrets/ssh/id_ed25519
#   4. Ensure public key is in server's ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
#
# Generate new key pair:
#   ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -f secrets/ssh/id_ed25519 -C "geostat-deploy"
#   ssh-copy-id -i secrets/ssh/id_ed25519.pub user@host
